  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>spaces</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>There are spaces in between</l>
          <l>Neither here, neither there,</l>
          <l>They could be anywhere,</l>
          <l>This is where I like to live,</l>
          <l>close to freedom,</l>
          <l>I create my own kingdom.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>They say that home is where the heart is</l>
          <l>But I'm all alone</l>
          <l>Without a home</l>
          <l>I've got a homeless heart, or a heartless home,</l>
          <l>And that's just the way I want it.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>I have loved many people,</l>
          <l>Both from east, and from west,</l>
          <l>It's hard to choose what I like best.</l>
          <l>I'm a citizen of the world,</l>
          <l>Working hard, loving harder,</l>
          <l>I'm a knight in shining armor.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>They say that home is where the heart is</l>
          <l>But I'm all alone</l>
          <l>Without a home</l>
          <l>I've got a homeless heart, or a heartless home</l>
          <l>And that's just the way I want it.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>Sometimes I get lost</l>
          <l>And it's hard to find</l>
          <l>The earth</l>
          <l>The ground</l>
          <l>The roots of my tree</l>
          <l>And I'm just floating in the wind</l>
          <l>Waiting to see where it takes me</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>Perhaps one day I'll find a home,</l>
          <l>Settle down, once and for all,</l>
          <l>But I doubt it, afterall….</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
